{"tid":1810312,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"新年新氣候 - 開始宣傳新年冇利是「和你封」行動","createTime":"2020-01-03T18:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T08:57:51.000Z","uid":196227,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"be778bf238e4925a10e3072092f5f6fa5aaee147","tid":1810312,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:21:56.000Z","msg":"新年冇利是唔代表真係唔洗派<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係針對最大得益既垃圾保安<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行動代號（1） - 和你封（利是）<br />\n- 有困難小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（相信好多人一直派緊，好多謝各位家長付出）<br />\n<br />\n- 真保安<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係呢場抗爭的確有小數保安有盡力，亦因為咁承受咗唔小壓力。我們除咗感謝終於可以大大力比封利是佢。 <br />\n至於班假保安，利是塞文宣激撚死佢地啦。<br />\n<br />\n- 黃店黃絲職員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我們罰黃店既同時，職員仔其實增加緊工作量。係時候罰撚埋佢地。<br />\n（其實好多人以為飲食零售會收到好多利是，事實上除咗上咗年紀既熟客會比，基本冇咩利是收。）<br />\n記住係黃職員，大家去慣附近嗰幾間，實知邊個真黃。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n～～～～～～～～～重點呀<br />\n<br />\n行動代號（2） - 和你封（文宣）<br />\n大家一定覺得樓下保安好唔順眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n住香港地比垃圾政府搞到咁窮<br />\n今年花紅一定小咗，仲封比班賣主犬托柒<br />\n利是塞文宣教育佢地仲實際～<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信大家情願封比有困難既小朋友"},{"pid":"21a01547baddba44c5d6fa5ea8cc9d3cb9aee618","tid":1810312,"uid":178214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:23:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"15b55ee6e5e49dacddb8ace9e071a9bc71336e9b","tid":1810312,"uid":196227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:26:20.000Z","msg":"呢個活動其實係黃色經濟圈分支<br />\n我們要重擊埋班垃圾保安<br />\n<br />\n以我生存30幾年所知<br />\n保安收利是係講緊幾倍花紅黎<br />\n仲要係平民區住宅保安每封收10-20蚊。<br />\n<br />\n有錢人地方不能想像<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7658edace1c66e919480269bef49ef023fc77dc","tid":1810312,"uid":296866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:27:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"766ca4d69f21e054fc1261c433a8fa14350c6b75","tid":1810312,"uid":196227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:31:45.000Z","msg":"有錢既就去做和你派-利是<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇錢既都可以一嘗派利是既感覺，分享快樂好重要<br />\n和你封 - 文宣好啱你地<br />\n又可以清晒屋企幾十年既利是封存貨<br />\n真正既物盡其用<br />\n封利是仲開心過收嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31901a9b2d1e3382803d6f27cf994bc06677600f","tid":1810312,"uid":196227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:37:54.000Z","msg":"估唔到我呢個一事無成既30歲肥仔<br />\n<br />\n可以係有生之年封利是比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c0b6835157b56cffb477fe1a91d206d5903c88","tid":1810312,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:38:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b22e1510666842d0118ddeeba2418d58b4b42312","tid":1810312,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7c0b6835157b56cffb477fe1a91d206d5903c88","tid":1810312,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:38:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:40:01.000Z","msg":"屌，有時間去分化責怪<br />\n不如去諗新活動，改善之處啦<br />\n<br />\n利申講緊班撚屌不是你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359c6d7a32bb5a5601d3319cadb2de291ed2650d","tid":1810312,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:42:01.000Z","msg":"大家，係時候開始「新年冇利是」文宣宣傳啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1765165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1765165</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n可以參考呢個post入面既事延伸去做<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc95a0caafcf334207115bcc30eee880e02e7fc8","tid":1810312,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:43:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f66060f954176f25669494eaf0ec3fe042bd301","tid":1810312,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:57:51.000Z","msg":"冇人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}